biography.text: Dj Yo! produced the remix for “love nwantiti (feat. Dj Yo! & AX'EL) [Remix]” from Nigeria’s CKay, one of the most popular remixes ever. His remix re-energized CKay’s single when Dj Yo!'s version became viral on Tik Tok.
